{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"66dcc39f3f","title":"毛泽东在《人民日报》发表《关于胡风反党集团的第二批材料》的编者按语稿中加写的两段话","origin":"原载一九五五年五月二十四日《人民日报》。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"cb8edcbea3","index":0,"year":1955,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"66dcc39f3f"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"d4ae0c1f37","type":"title","text":"毛泽东在《人民日报》发表《关于胡风反党集团的第二批材料》的编者按语稿中加写的两段话","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"66dcc39f3f"},{"id":"530f615a69","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"66dcc39f3f"},{"id":"28fa2e73b9","type":"subtitle","text":"一","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"66dcc39f3f"},{"id":"4a2c049a21","type":"paragraph","text":"有些同情胡风或者口头上反对胡风但内心是同情胡风的人们在说，那些材料大都是解放以前的，不能据此定罪。那末，好吧，现在请看第二批材料。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"66dcc39f3f"},{"id":"1dde79264c","type":"subtitle","text":"二","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"66dcc39f3f"},{"id":"47c786e1ba","type":"paragraph","text":"反革命的胡风分子同其他公开的或暗藏的反革命分子一样，他们是把希望寄托在反革命政权的复辟和人民革命政权的倒台的。他们认为，这就是他们要“等待”的“时机”。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"66dcc39f3f"}],"page":{"id":"16177aee52","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"66dcc39f3f","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}